text: I wonder if people (and us) are trying to be too cute with lazav
Like maybe it would be better as some sort of good creature deck and lazav is just gravy. Seems like the creatures to enable lazav are all shit and you have to play a bunch of trash cards
I see it as three buckets that you want to fill: evasion, value and pay off
Fill to your needs for your meta
We might be doing the cute things, but that’s because we all want to do our own payoffs
The evasion and value is where the meat of the deck is going to be
Evasion is clearly the most important one too, got to get around all the nasty stuff
I think a good creature deck helmed by Lazav would need to run creatures that were almost exclusively CMC<3.
